org.lindbergframework.persistence.sql
Class XmlSqlCommandResolver

java.lang.Object
  org.lindbergframework.persistence.sql.XmlSqlCommandResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
LinpConfigurationInitializer, SqlCommandResolver
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClassPathXmlSqlCommandResolver
public class XmlSqlCommandResolver
extends Object
implements SqlCommandResolver, LinpConfigurationInitializer

Sql command resolver implementation to work with XML mapping for sql commands. The XML schema is defined in http://www.lindbergframework.org/schema/linp-sqlMapping.xsd

Author:
Victor Lindberg
